"title": "2425: gospel, requirements of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2425: gospel, requirements of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The gospel demands an obedient response to all that God has done for humanity in Jesus Christ. This includes faith in God, trust in the work of Jesus Christ, the repenting of sin, being baptised, and becoming like Christ through discipleship.</p>\n<h2>The requirement of faith</h2>\n<h3>Belief in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:38\">JHN 10:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25-John11:27\">JHN 11:25–11:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:8-John14:11\">JHN 14:8–14:11</a></p>\n<h3>Trust in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14-John3:16\">JHN 3:14–3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12-John1:13\">JHN 1:12–1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:37-John7:39\">JHN 7:37–7:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:31\">JHN 20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38-Acts13:39\">ACT 13:38–13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:31\">ACT 16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:22\">ROM 3:22</a></p>\n<h2>The requirement of repentance</h2>\n<h3>A conscious change of mind and heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:17-Acts3:20\">ACT 3:17–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:17\">PSA 51:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:12-Jer3:13\">JER 3:12–3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:16\">JER 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:13-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:13–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a></p>\n<h3>Turning away from sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:22\">ACT 8:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:14\">PSA 34:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:20\">ISA 59:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:4-Jer25:6\">JER 25:4–25:6</a></p>\n<h3>Turning towards God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:21\">ACT 20:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:29-Deut4:31\">DEU 4:29–4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:8-Deut30:10\">DEU 30:8–30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:21-Isa44:22\">ISA 44:21–44:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6-Isa55:7\">ISA 55:6–55:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:1-Hos14:2\">HOS 14:1–14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8-Jas4:10\">JAS 4:8–4:10</a></p>\n<h2>The requirement of baptism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:18–28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:12\">ACT 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:36-Acts8:38\">ACT 8:36–8:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:47-Acts10:48\">ACT 10:47–10:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:1-Acts19:5\">ACT 19:1–19:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:16\">ACT 22:16</a></p>\n<h2>The requirement of public confession of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:9–10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:32\">MAT 10:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:8-Luke12:9\">LUK 12:8–12:9</a></p>\n<h2>The requirement of discipleship</h2>\n<h3>Willingness to learn from Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:28–11:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:14-John13:15\">JHN 13:14–13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a></p>\n<h3>Willingness to obey Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:3-1John2:6\">1JN 2:3–2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:21-1John3:24\">1JN 3:21–3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:3\">1JN 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:6\">2JN 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Willingness to suffer for the sake of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:21-Acts14:22\">ACT 14:21–14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:29\">PHP 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10-2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:10–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2\">JAS 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:14\">1PE 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:12–4:19</a></p>",
